I"7<p>Lead role for UX design projects.<br />
Work closely with product and support teams to understand business and user goals and help to translate this into designs that meet the needs of both.<br />
Work closely with engineering team to understand technical boundaries and ensure design integrity during development.<br />
Produce high quality interaction design artefacts: user flows, wireframes and mock-ups.<br />
Organize usability tests and create simple prototypes for testing.<br />
Participate in the creation of usability design standards and patterns.</p>
